      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle is offered in showroom condition, exhibiting a level of preservation that satisfies the most exacting standards of excellence. Every facet, from the flawless exterior luster to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of meticulous maintenance and climate-controlled stewardship. Mechanically superior and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a masterpiece of engineering in its absolute prime.",
      "price": 46500.0,
