      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014looks and feels just like it did when it first left the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for the road, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
